{"tid":952073,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯願付 4 億 硬撬普捷天奴","createTime":"2018-12-22T20:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T14:32:09.000Z","uid":123335,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b911e5f5a86af2d22f25c639b1d988149d7767a3","tid":952073,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T20:15:28.000Z","msg":"曼聯上周辭退摩連奴，由蘇斯克查暫掌帥印，但球會仍在物色來季正式接任人選。據悉紅魔在帥位人選上仍然只有熱刺領隊普捷天奴一人，不過要得到普帥價值不菲，紅魔需要賠償達4,200萬鎊（約4億港元）予熱刺。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯辭退摩佬後找來蘇斯克查暫代看守領隊至季尾，但正式帥位仍然懸空，據報球會有意挖角熱刺領隊普捷天奴，他今夏與熱刺簽下850萬鎊的5年長約，因此紅魔至少需向熱刺支付4,200萬鎊違約金買斷其合約，再加上領隊薪酬，或成球壇上費用最昂貴的易帥交易。不過據稱紅魔已做好準備，球隊高層均認為巨額買入普捷天奴物有所值，但球會仍需面對激烈競爭，事關西甲球隊皇家馬德里亦有意羅致普帥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20181223/59060163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181223%2F59060163&d=LH01F22bqoHxxGzYtuV5gLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b674af20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181223%2F59060163&h=fe7b199e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20181223/59060163</a>"},{"pid":"9f90080fae216fe3b6dec52e6badf336901c823a","tid":952073,"uid":134997,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T21:45:33.000Z","msg":"心諗4億我獌不如回購c朗+買尼馬<br />\n點知係港紙"},{"pid":"fa314caf07713d93ffddc0194087154f3d88eedf","tid":952073,"uid":24524,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9f90080fae216fe3b6dec52e6badf336901c823a","tid":952073,"uid":134997,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T21:45:33.000Z","msg":"心諗4億我獌不如回購c朗+買尼馬<br />\n點知係港紙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T21:50:31.000Z","msg":"4000萬買個領隊 分分鐘值過買10個8000萬球員"},{"pid":"6174d17cc74c7b64c3dd2f2f0917dccd7166e8e1","tid":952073,"uid":143667,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T22:16:29.000Z","msg":"普巴批准未先<img src=\"/assets/fac